{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Playful SaaS</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f0f0;\n            color: #333;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #e53935; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        .shapes div {\n            position: absolute;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n        .shape1 {\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 150px;\n            top: 50px;\n            left: 10%;\n            animation: float 5s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .shape2 {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            bottom: 30px;\n            right: 15%;\n            animation: float 7s infinite ease-in-out -2s;\n        }\n        .shape3 {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            top: 20%;\n            right: 40%;\n            animation: float 6s infinite ease-in-out -1s;\n        }\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }\n            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }\n            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: #e53935;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fdf6f6;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #c62828;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background-color: #e53935; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #e53935;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f0f0;\n            color: #c62828;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #c62828;\n            color: #f8f0f0;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .footer-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .features h2, .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .feature-item h3 {\n                font-size: 1.5em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                font-size: 1em;\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n            }\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p, .features h2, .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .feature-item h3 {\n                font-size: 1.3em;\n            }\n            .feature-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"shapes\">\n            <div class=\"shape1\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape2\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape3\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1>Your Awesome SaaS!</h1>\n            <p>Revolutionize your workflow with a splash of fun and a whole lot of efficiency. We make complex tasks feel like a breeze.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <h2>What Makes Us Sparkle?</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Playful Interface</h3>\n                <p>Navigate with ease through a design that's as intuitive as it is delightful. No more boring dashboards!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Boost Your Fun</h3>\n                <p>Our tools aren't just productive; they're designed to bring a smile to your face while you conquer your goals.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Effortless Integration</h3>\n                <p>Seamlessly connect with your existing tools. We play well with others!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Always Improving</h3>\n                <p>We're constantly adding new features and making things even better, like a magic trick!</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Add Some Zing?</h2>\n        <p>Join thousands of happy users and transform your work with a touch of playfulness.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Your Free Trial Now!</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"footer-content\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Playful SaaS. All rights reserved. <br> We're just getting started!</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for any future interactivity if needed\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            console.log(\"Playful SaaS website loaded!\");\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}